title: New Jersey Bridges
description:
This point data set is a spatial respresentation are bridges in New Jersey. It was created by the New Jersey Department of Transportation GIS Unit from the PONTIS Table -  latitude/longitude coordinates,  compiled by the New Jersey Department of Transportation GIS Office.

title: DVRPC Existing Bike Stress LTS
description: Shows assigned level of traffic stress based on number of lanes, effective speed, and presence/type of bicycle facility.
